actuarial HR for CoMMpass data

actuarial hazard function

act.haz.se <- function(data, time, event, class){
  data <- as.data.frame(data)
  time <- data[,time]
  event <- data[,event]
  class <- data[,class]
  temp_sdf <- survdiff(Surv(time, event) ~ class)
  HR <- (temp_sdf$obs[2]/temp_sdf$exp[2])/(temp_sdf$obs[1]/temp_sdf$exp[1])
  SE <- sqrt(1/temp_sdf$exp[1] + 1/temp_sdf$exp[2])
  CIL <- exp(log(HR)-(1.96*SE))
  CIU <- exp(log(HR)+(1.96*SE))
  return(c(hr=HR,se.ln.hr=SE,conf.low=CIL,conf.up=CIU))
}
gmm2_cmps_thr_HR <- act.haz.se(cmps_rset_data, "ttcos", "censos", "gmm2_class")
